#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_beds/api.lua:104
msgid "Beds allow you to sleep at night and make the time pass faster."
msgstr ""
"Kasur memungkinkan Anda tidur di malam hari dan membuat waktu berlalu lebih "
"cepat."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_beds/api.lua:105
msgid ""
"To use a bed, stand close to it and right-click the bed to sleep in it. "
"Sleeping only works when the sun sets, at night or during a thunderstorm. "
"The bed must also be clear of any danger."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menggunakan kasur, berdirilah di dekatnya dan klik kanan untuk tidur. "
"Tidur hanya dapat dilakukan saat matahari terbenam, di malam hari, atau saat "
"badai petir. Kasur juga harus aman jauh dari ancaman apapun."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_beds/api.lua:107
msgid ""
"You have heard of other worlds in which a bed would set the start point for "
"your next life. But this world is not one of them."
msgstr ""
"Kamu pernah mendengar tentang dunia lain di mana tempat tidur akan menjadi "
"titik awal kehidupan kamu selanjutnya. Namun, dunia ini bukanlah salah "
"satunya."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_beds/api.lua:109
msgid ""
"By using a bed, you set the starting point for your next life. If you die, "
"you will start your next life at this bed, unless it is obstructed or "
"destroyed."
msgstr ""
"Dengan memakai kasur, kamu akan menggunakannya untuk posisi awal hidup, Jika "
"kamu mati, kamu akan memulai kembali dari tempat tidur, kecuali kasur tidak "
"bisa diakses atau telah dihancurkan."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_beds/api.lua:112
msgid ""
"In this world, going to bed won't skip the night, but it will skip "
"thunderstorms."
msgstr ""
"Dalam dunia ini, pergi ke tempat tidur tidak akan melewati malam, namun akan "
"melewati badai petir."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_beds/api.lua:114
msgid ""
"Sleeping allows you to skip the night. The night is skipped when all players "
"in this world went to sleep. The night is skipped after sleeping for a few "
"seconds. Thunderstorms can be skipped in the same manner."
msgstr ""
"Tidur memungkinkan kamu untuk melewati malam. Malam akan terlewati begitu "
"saja ketika semua pemain tidur. Malam akan berlalu dalam beberapa detik "
"setelah tidur. Badai petir pun juga akan berlalu."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_beds/api.lua:129
msgid "Allows you to sleep"
msgstr "Memungkinkan kamu untuk tidur"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_beds/beds.lua:21
msgid "Bed"
msgstr "Kasur"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_beds/functions.lua:85
#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_beds/respawn_anchor.lua:27
msgid "New respawn position set!"
msgstr "Posisi bangkit telah diatur!"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_beds/functions.lua:90
msgid "You can only sleep at night or during a thunderstorm."
msgstr "Kamu hanya bisa tidur saat malam atau sedang badai petir."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_beds/functions.lua:95
msgid "You can't sleep, the bed's too far away!"
msgstr "Tidak bisa tidur, kasur terlalu jauh!"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_beds/functions.lua:100
msgid "This bed is already occupied!"
msgstr "Kasur sudah ada yang punya!"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_beds/functions.lua:113
msgid "You can't sleep now, monsters are nearby!"
msgstr "Kamu tidak bisa tidur sekarang, banyak monster mendekat!"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_beds/functions.lua:158
msgid "You can't sleep, the bed is obstructed!"
msgstr "Kamu tidak bisa tidur, kasurnya terhalang!"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_beds/functions.lua:160
msgid "It's too dangerous to sleep here!"
msgstr "Terlalu berbahaya tidur disini!"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_beds/functions.lua:213
msgid "Leave bed"
msgstr "Tinggalkan kasur"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_beds/functions.lua:214
msgid "Abort sleep"
msgstr "Batalkan tidur"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_beds/functions.lua:217
msgid "Chat:"
msgstr "Mengobrol:"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_beds/functions.lua:218
msgid "send!"
msgstr "kirim!"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_beds/functions.lua:229
msgid "Players in bed: @1/@2"
msgstr "Pemain di tempat tidur: @1/@2"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_beds/functions.lua:231 mods/ITEMS/mcl_beds/functions.lua:258
msgid "Note: Night skip is disabled."
msgstr "Catatan: Melewati malam dinonaktifkan."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_beds/functions.lua:235 mods/ITEMS/mcl_beds/functions.lua:254
msgid "You're sleeping."
msgstr "Kamu sedang tidur."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_beds/functions.lua:241
msgid "You will fall asleep when all players are in bed."
msgstr "Kamu akan tertidur saat semua pemain sudah berada di kasur."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_beds/functions.lua:243
msgid "You will fall asleep when @1% of all players are in bed."
msgstr "Kamu akan tertidur saat @1% dari semua pemain berada di kasur."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_beds/functions.lua:258
msgid "You're in bed."
msgstr "Kamu berada di kasur."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_beds/functions.lua:379
msgid "@1/@2 players currently in bed."
msgstr "@1/@2 pemain saat ini berada di kasur."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_beds/functions.lua:452
msgid "You exceeded the maximum number of messages per 10 seconds!"
msgstr "Kamu melebihi batas maksimal pesan per 10 detik!"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_beds/functions.lua:461
msgid ""
"You are missing the 'shout' privilege! It's required in order to talk in "
"chat..."
msgstr ""
"Kamu tidak memiliki hak 'shout'! Ini dibutuhkan untuk bisa berbicara di "
"obrolan..."

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_beds/functions.lua:480
msgid ""
"Sorry, but you have to wait @1 seconds until you may use this button again!"
msgstr "Maaf, kamu harus menunggu @1 detik untuk bisa memakai tombol ini lagi!"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_beds/functions.lua:486
msgid "Hey! Would you guys mind sleeping?"
msgstr "Hei! Kalian ga keberatan untuk tidur?"

